INSERT INTO `news` VALUES ('A1401','爱上飞行 自由翱翔','/upload/NEWS/A1401/20170704154522_108_O.JPG','1','TYPE1','N','<p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">最本质的问题：拥有和驾驶一个</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的美妙之处在哪？</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Dan\r\nJohnson</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（丹•约翰逊），</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LAMA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（轻型飞机制造商协会）的总裁</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">, </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">运动型飞机资深评论家，带着我们滑行，与我们谈论</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">21</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">世纪的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（轻型运动飞机）。</span>&nbsp;</p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>“</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">有两种飞行员”他说，“长途飞行，和娱乐飞行。确实，我们在两者之间来回。但是你天生不是这个就是那个”</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">长途者们驾驶飞机为去某地。娱乐者们则驾驶飞机游玩，俯瞰美丽的大地，或飞舞在这无尽的天空。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">约翰逊认为专注的长途者数量上更少一些。“但是娱乐飞行者们呢？他们会绕着本地的区域各种飞，享受偏航的快乐。”</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>“</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">这”约翰逊总结说，“为人们展示了享受驾驶轻型运动飞机的更大的潜力。”</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">小空间的独奏&nbsp;</p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">研究显示飞机上，包括四座和六座的，每一飞行小时平均有</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1.6</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">位乘员。这意味着大约一半的时间，我们都是“单”飞。除了那些超过</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">120</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">节的快速、重型牵引</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">GA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">航班，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">提供更高效的、更实惠的休闲的飞行时光。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">许多</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">也可以不错地处理长途飞行。我曾在</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Dakota Cub</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">中完成飞行</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1200</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">英里，也曾在</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Evektor Max</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">中完成</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">16</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">小时，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1700</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">英里的环形旅行。“</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的认证是其他类别无法提供的最好的东西</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"> ”</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><br></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 11pt;\">特色，优势…和挑战</p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">轻型运动飞机</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2004</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">年由</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">FAA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（美国联邦航空局）授权，它并不很像以前我们见过的任何东西。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">•LSA</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的购买价格，全新的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">比许多二手的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">GA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">飞机更实惠。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">•LSA </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">是经过</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">ASTM</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">标准认证的制造商。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">•LSA </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">有着更低的运作与维修费用，更小的噪音，非常多的种类（</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">115</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">种型号）和前沿的科技。</span>&nbsp;</p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">•LSA </span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">要求的是一个便利、低成本的运动飞机执照</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">•LSA </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">拥有者可以自己做轻度维修，并且可以学习课程以（保证）每年合法地运转和其他的检查。</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">•LSA </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">易于操作，并且它们都很舒服与安全。实际上，许多（</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">）装备机体降落伞。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">挑战：尽管</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">比一架</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">GA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">飞机便宜不少，但</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">还未用一架</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">40000</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元的飞机把我们导向节约——</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">GA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的应许之地（指的是，上帝赐给信徒得以繁衍后代的丰饶土地）。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">考虑：</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1970</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">年，一架</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Champ 2</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">座飞机费用为全国平均工资的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1.5</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">倍。今天，它的后裔，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Super Decathlon(</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">超级迪卡斯龙</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">)</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">，费用为</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">164000</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元，年收入的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">3.65</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">倍，差不多跟最贵的复合</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">一样…而一个全新的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cessna172 </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">花费超过</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">300000</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元——年收入的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">7</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">倍！</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">更便宜——但对很多人来说仍是遥不可及。一个解决方案</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">——</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">急需文化思维模式的转变</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">——</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">就是共享所有权。像</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Let’s\r\nFly</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（让我们飞）、</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Aircraft Partnership Association</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（飞机合作协会），这样的组织，（最近获得飞行员协会承认并且已经有</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1000</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">名会员）和再度流行的飞行俱乐部将再次帮助卖家享受拥有飞机的好处——花费只等于买一辆新车。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">我们说的是一架新的，未使用的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">。并且随着经济重创的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2000</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美国注册</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">机队的迅速扩大，预计更便宜的“二手”</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">会开始出现。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: SimSun; font-size: 11pt;\">震颤的执照</p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">当然，更轻的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">比</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">GA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">飞机更容易受到大气的影响。像</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cubs</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">和以前的教练员，会需要学生们过去学到的更好的飞行技术。这是件好事。运动型（飞机的）飞机员也需要更注意天气。另一件好事。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>“</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">大部分我的学生六十岁以后拿到他们的第一个飞行执照，花费少于</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">20</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">小时做复式操纵飞行训练”统计显示大部分的飞行员平均每月花费</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">4</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">到</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">8</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">个小时。这是典型的“经历者”飞行。‘驾照’健康认证—可以说是运动飞行员概念里最解放性的好处</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">—</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">绝不是让飞行员规避危害到安全的健康问题的方法。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>“</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">它确实帮助飞行员保持更长的飞行员状态”</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Dan Johnson</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（丹•约翰逊）评述道，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">“</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（但）我很愿意看到</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">FAA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（美国联邦航空局）撤回强制执行的、对所有类别轻型飞机飞行的（</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">FAA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的）健康认证”。没有统计说明健康是重大威胁：所有飞行意外中它们只影响不到</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1%</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的代表</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">跟那些每天工作都与</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">打交道并乐在其中的人相比，谁更会为</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">唱赞歌呢？</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Mike Zidziunas</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（迈克•吉浦）的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（公司）蓬勃发展，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Breezer Aircraft USA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（美国冰锐飞机）在佛罗里达中部，有三种全金属、德国制造冰锐</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">II </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">低翼锋忙着训练与租赁。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>“</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">大部分我的学生六十岁以后拿到他们的第一个飞行执照，他们花费少于</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">20</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">小时做复式操纵飞行训练”</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Mike\r\nZ </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（迈克•吉）说到。这令人印象深刻：运动型（飞机）飞行员规则约束最少</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">20</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">小时（复式和单式），但是</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">35-40</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">小时是典型的。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">虽然轻型运动飞机比其他飞机相对便宜，对于一些飞行员来说，还是遥不可及。共享所有权为解决此问题提供了方法。“我最年长的学生，他</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">85</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">岁了，已经在投入</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">350</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">个小时在他的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Ercoupe</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">上”他补充道。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Mike Z </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（迈克•吉）的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">分销商</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">/</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">经销商</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">/</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">飞行学校是这个国家最老的。“</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2005</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">年以来，我们没有一起单一事故，甚至爆胎都没有！”三分之一他的运动型飞行持照者会继续取得他们私人飞机驾驶执照。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Lou Mancuso</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（卢•曼库索），有</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">7000</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">小时的飞行教官执照，提供</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">和</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">GA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">飞行训练。他的纽约长岛的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Mid Island Air Service</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（中岛空中服务）训练</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">SportCruiser</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">、</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Remos GX</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">和</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cessna Skycatcher</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">。他的机群中也有</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cessna</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（赛纳斯）</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"> </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">和</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Piper GA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（派珀</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">GA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">），所以他比更多人知道它们相对的优点。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>“LSA</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">飞机和</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"> ‘</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">驾照’健康认证是其他类别无法提供的最好的东西。”</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Lou Mancuso</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（卢•曼库索）说到，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">“</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">顾客对停止飞行的前景感到伤心。现在他们回来了。</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">”</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Mancuso</span><span style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（曼库索）的学生年龄范围很广“从很年轻的到很年长的都有，我让大家都得到了运动型飞行员执照。我们不讨论私人（飞行执照）。现在我们的中途退出率比以前要低多了。”</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>“LSA</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">将会修补飞行员数量减少的问题”</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Mancuso</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（曼库索）补充道，“经历</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">70</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">小时私人飞行执照训练是一个很大的投入，特别是在拥挤的，有塔的飞机场。运动型飞行课程只要</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">30</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">到</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">40</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">小时将会使情况扭转。”</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Mancuso</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（曼库索）说“</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">租赁、保养和维修便宜多了。零件也不贵：一个推进器花费</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2000</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元；</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cessna</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（赛纳斯）的则要</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">4300</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元。火花塞</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">4</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元而不是</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">25</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元。我们每</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">100</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">小时就换个新火花塞而不是清理它们。电子点火</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Rotax</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（路达思）如此的美妙：两投掷距离叶片。所有老式科技，如交流发电机、传动带，可破裂的支架，都没了。</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Rotax</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（路达思）的导向叶片压气机永没有问题。”</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>“LSA</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">也比</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">GA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">飞机更安全”</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Mancuso</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（曼库索）继续说，“驾驶</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Beech Musketeer</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">我们曾有出现引擎故障。勉强停在了停机坪。我的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">比它飞更高</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">4:1</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">，比</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cessna 152 </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">更高</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">3:1</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">。</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">用更好的引擎关闭滑翔率更快速到达高度。”</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>“LSA </span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">在航电设备上也有进展，并以</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">75%</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的折扣超越有证仪表。每过一个月，我都能了解到</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的新亮点，这让我感到兴奋。”</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Mancuso</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（曼库索）说。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Shelley Wozniak</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（雪梨•沃兹尼亚克）</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">, </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">一位来自佛罗里达斯图尔特的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Remos GX</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">拥有者，回应</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Mancuso</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的热情。她也教授</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">。“我飞过了</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">GA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">飞机、直升机和</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">后，在</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">58</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">岁开始教课。我有</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Aviator II model</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（飞行员</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">II</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">号）所以我也教仪器导航飞行。它操作起来便宜的多。”</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Wozniak</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（沃兹尼亚克）兴奋地补充道：“我带两个大男爵飞行员兜风。他俩很紧张……知道我们飞起来。接着他们就很兴奋了！他们也想买一架；他们不能相信这是多么有趣。这是一个对人们飞翔来说美好的时代。轻型运动（飞机）太令人惊喜了。我</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">13</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">岁的时候开始驾驶</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">J3</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">。这些是那种飞行的现代版的。我给所有人推荐</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LSA</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">。”</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Dillard \"Doc\"\r\nWilliams</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（德拉迪•威廉）爱驾驶他的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Remos G3 </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">穿越全国和天空露营：“我已经用它飞了</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1250</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">个小时，只有五个州没飞过。这是我第十七架飞机。”他也拥有超轻型飞机和</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cessna 182</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（赛纳斯）系列</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Williams</span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（威廉）折起</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Remos</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的机翼，装载到他的拖车上，并去寻找冒险。“拖车变成了我的旅馆。我找到了一个地方有</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">300</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">英尺土路，卸载，起飞，接着降落，欣赏日落，吃着牛排，喝着加利福尼亚解百纳葡萄酒——不是露营食物哦！</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">”</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">一般燃料燃烧：</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">50%</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">巡航时</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">3.5</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">加仑每小时。“</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">182</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">是</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">13gph</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">，”</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Williams (</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">威廉</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">)</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">说</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">. </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">单单是燃料就每小时省</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">70</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元—</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Rotax</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（路达思）喜欢更便宜的车用燃料。</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<br></p>','A0001','2017-07-04 15:44:35','A0001','2017-07-04 16:51:49'), ('A1403','成为飞行员的伟大时刻到来了','/upload/NEWS/A1403/20170704155253_790_O.JPG','1','TYPE1','N','\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">成为飞行员的伟大时刻到来了。安飞客接受客户的订制化服务，如您对某种轻型飞机有个性化的需求。安飞客将提供专业的服务，支持您实现伟大的梦想。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">随着经济政策方面得到落实，通用航空大亨（</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cessna</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">和派珀）更多地以空中捕手和派珀运动型飞机的姿态显示它的强大力量，并找到了回家之路。新的小型轻型运动型飞机</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">-111</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">型在我们交付印刷的时候不断生产。期间，飞行学校用它们日渐增多的轻型运动型飞机吸引新的学生。很长时间以来的市场先行者们（</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Flight Design, Legend Cub, CubCrafters,\r\nTecnam, Remos</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">）的竞争仍然很激烈，毕竟不断有新的竞争者前来分一杯羹。当然这也是买家的市场。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">轻型运动型飞机的安全性记录一直保持完美，尽管如此，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">2004</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">年，美国材料实验协会一致认证程序和运动型飞行员准则令其合法化，这对于联邦航空局来说，在获得大众信任方面也是一个飞跃，且这一切似乎都起了作用。对于轻型运动型的乐观的前景的期盼完全是夸张的。即使度过了艰难的“货币市场危机”，大部分生产商，无论是国内的还剩国外的，尽力在此行业中挣扎。那意味着你更难做决定，因为已得到证实的设计仍然改善并刺激新的参与者进入这个市场。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">轻型运动型飞机，曾经是低成本飞行的希望，如今在价格方面却有了很大的上升。股份制组织如</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">LetsFly</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">和航空合作协会将坚决要购买的飞行员匹配为在乎的买家，甚至操作财政，保养和建机库——仅需要月分期付款。租赁也比较寻常，因为轻型运动型飞机的队伍在全国范围内扩大。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">THE\r\nLEADER BOARD</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">充足的预飞行：让我们叫做用来调查轻型运动型飞机多选择的工具。我们会从处于美国联邦航空局注册列表中的飞机开始【多亏</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Jan Fridrich</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（贾恩•弗雷德里奇），他为网站</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">www.bydanjohnson.com</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">编制了这份列表）。可以注意到列表中前</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">20</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">名占据了总销量的百分之八十五以上。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">Flight\r\nDesign</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><a href=\"http://www.flightdesignusa.com/\"><u><font color=\"#0066cc\">www.flightdesignusa.com</font></u></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">这个全碳纤维，德国制造的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">CTLS</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">仍然是优胜者，并没有落后的迹象，它在美国有超过</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">300</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">条注册记录。</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">FD</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的全金属</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">MC</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">，易于驾驭，有着超大空间，易于维修训练，它的主要目标人群是飞行学校里的人。</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"> </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">新增：</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">CT</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">拥有很棒的浮筒式包裹和一个全国范围内有着</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">40</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">家服务中心的坚固的网络系统。</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"> </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">全“玻璃”的电子飞行仪表系统有着丰富的选择性，包括</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Skyview</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">和</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Garmin\r\nG3X </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">控制板。价格</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">: 139,800</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">(CTLS);\r\n119,980</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">(CTLS </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">精简版</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">);\r\n118,083</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">(MC)</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">American\r\nLegend</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><a href=\"http://www.legend.aero/\"><u><font color=\"#0066cc\">www.legend.aero</font></u></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">紧跟着</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Flight Design</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的是美国头号制造商</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">American Legend,</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">它的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Legend Cub</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">最初是在原始版派珀</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cub J3</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">设计上获得持久信任的，它拥有</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cub</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">型升级的一流设计团队，包括</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Continetal O-200</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">（</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">100</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">马力）或者</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Jabiru 3300A(120</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">马力）的动力选择。机队也包括</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">AmphibCub (</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">浮筒式</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">), Classic J3 </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">和</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Texas Star E-</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">轻型运动型飞机改装型。选择：</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"> </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">复合型飞机，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Dynon,\r\nGarmin </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">和</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">TruTrak </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">玻璃式</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">. </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">价格</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">: 117,895</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">(Cub, </span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">开阔的通风帽</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">);\r\n159,000</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">(AmphibCub); 97,895</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">(Classic J3)</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">。</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"> </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">Piper\r\nAircraft</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><a href=\"http://www.piper.com/\"><u><font color=\"#0066cc\">www.piper.com</font></u></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">通过其积极的生产计划力跳跃到第三位的派珀飞机公司，它的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">PiperSport</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">是采用最初的</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">SportCruiser</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">，是富有运动感，性感的赢家。建于捷克共和国，在美国进行装配，它是飞行中的弱者，却有着令人印象深刻的速度</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">-</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">失速巡航速度（</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">26/120</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">节）的速度比。因其舒适，反应灵敏，和优良的性能（</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1200</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">英尺每分钟爬升，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">600\r\nnm</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">范围），</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">PiperSport</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">在今年年底可能成为头号轻型运动型飞机。价格：</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">119,000-139900</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元（三种型号）。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">CubCrafters</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><a href=\"http://www.cubcrafters.com/\"><u><font color=\"#0066cc\">www.cubcrafters.com</font></u></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">派珀</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cub</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">风格主宰美国总销量，占据了近</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">25%</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">的市场份额。</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">CubCrafters</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">是另一个重要原因，这要归功于碳纤维</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cub SS</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">和运动型</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cub\r\nS2</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">。</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">SS</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">配置了</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">ECI CC340</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">，有着</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">180</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">马力的发动机。这两款机型都采用了经典</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cub</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">风格且用碳纤维制作，有更宽敞的内部空间，机翼油箱和电动启动。选项包括苔原轮胎，浮筒式包裹，玻璃面板等。价格：</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">163280</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元（碳纤维</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cub\r\nSS</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">）</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">; 127500</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元（运动型</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">S2</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">）。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">Tecnam\r\nAircraft</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><a href=\"http://www.tecnam.net/\"><u><font color=\"#0066cc\">www.tecnam.net</font></u></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">意大利制造商</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Tecnam</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">已经在建成优质飞机中度过了</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">60</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">年。它的轻型运动型飞机生产线给所有人提供了一项东西：小驱逐型飞机和观光飞机（低翼</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">P2002 Sierra</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">，高机翼</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">P92Echo Classic</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">P2004Bravo De Luxe</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">）</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">;</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">一个友好的，坚固的教练机（</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">P92Eaglet</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">）和豪华的复合材料</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">/</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">金属材料的具有</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">48</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">英寸宽的客舱和</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">120</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">节的巡航速度的观光飞机</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">P2008</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">。拓展经销商</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">/</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">培训</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">/</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">服务网络和其它众多选项，使</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Tecnam</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">成为值得尊敬的竞争者。价格：</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">109,999-169</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">999</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元（取决于型号和选项）。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-famil