 Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">Paradise\r\nAircraft</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><a href=\"http://www.paradiseaircraft.us/\"><u><font color=\"#0066cc\">www.paradiseaircraft.us</font></u></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11pt;\"><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">天堂</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">P-1</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">是一种流行的经过巴西认证的在</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">1999</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">年进行首飞的飞机，它美国组装，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">ASTM</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">认证的轻型运动型飞机版。最初是四座，双座高边锋有很多的行李空间。总的说来，这是一个坚实的，温顺的，令人愉快的用来飞行的飞机，用铬钼钢管和铝皮构造，还有坚固的铝合金弹簧传动装置，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Amsafe</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">安全带安全气囊，双线圈，可操纵的前轮和一些航空电子设备包。价格：</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">108</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">，</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">830</span><span lang=\"en-US\" style=\"font-family: SimSun;\">美元。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p lang=\"zh-CN\" style=\"margin: 0in; font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;\"